data.description: Embrace the charm of this delightful ranch home located in the desirable Waldo neighborhood! Boasting 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, this residence offers over 1,000 square feet of comfortable living space on the main level. The heart of this home, the cozy living area, invites you to unwind and enjoy the warmth of the space. The unfinished basement presents a blank canvas, providing an opportunity to tailor it to your unique preferences—whether as additional living space, a recreation room, or simply extra storage. Outside, the property sprawls over a quarter-acre lot, offering ample space for outdoor activities and entertaining. Let the kids play freely in the expansive yard or envision transforming it into your own oasis. This ranch home in Waldo is not just a house; it's an invitation to create lasting memories and make a cherished place uniquely yours. **After Repair Value - $265-275k** Don't miss your chance to build equity!
